OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FOften cloudy
OL,6,Fwith further outbreaks of mostly light
OL,7,Fand patchy drizzle during the evening,
OL,8,Fwith clear spells following for a
OL,9,Ftime. Turning cloudier and breezier
OL,10,Fovernight with a band of rain arriving
OL,11,Ffrom the west during the early hours.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FRain soon clearing to the
OL,14,Feast tomorrow with sunny spells and
OL,15,Fblustery showers following. These
OL,16,Flocally heavy with hail and a risk of
OL,17,Fthunder by the afternoon. Cooler and
OL,18,Fwindier.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
